Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:17.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go scarin' me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:04.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you? Weren't we heading to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:08.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but I smelled somethin' {\i1}really{\i0} freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The trees around him are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:14.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're dieing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that his magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't see that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:37.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but this island belongs to our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go bustin' in on our exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've... grown up nice and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to meet you, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He punched him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured that's what he'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not ready yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you can't yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,State your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't want to kill anyone anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But your were the only one who could have stopped me, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy takes creepy to a whole new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that black wave from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:13.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's magic that steals away life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine... But he...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's turned black.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to this scarf I got from Igneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Igneel's scarf took the brunt of it to protect Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:39.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to continue being rejected by the world again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical power... This pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:05.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it him? Is he here on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:25.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, a new danger is fast approaching Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:35.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart, one corner of the Baram Alliance, the strongest power among the Dark Guilds...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:44.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them can be seen the figure of Ultear, once an aide to Jellal who has fought Natsu and the others previously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:50.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally found you... Seems like you're still asleep, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:55.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the time has come, Master Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That man stepped forth on this land long ago, perfected Black Magic, gave birth to countless demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and plunged the world into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:16.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful, and most evil man in the history of the Magic World...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Wizard Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the day finally come when I can reach out and touch the deepest depths of magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:34.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change course to head to the fairy's island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:41.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare that bastard do this to Igneel's scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I wear a black scarf with dark clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a fashion faux pas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:50.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's picky about his coordination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd a thunk it. {going too far?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, what about the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With that freaky guy wandering around, it's no time for tests, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's most definitely the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Man, I will not back away from this exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am my big sister's little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a duty to become S class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He really was freaky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He cried all of a sudden, and killed those trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you sure have a lot of weird friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ain't my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't seem like he wanted to be your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue on with the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go, Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:40.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}thought{\i0} I told you not to order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I return and report this at once? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:54.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First I've got to make sure of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the time finally come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The day the legendary Black Wizard Zeref is resurrected...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the necessary keys already lie in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will awake something from within Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:20.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:25.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizards' Guild in Fiore Kingdom that currently holds the strongest position, Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the guilds that did in Oracion Seis, one of the members of the Baram Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the most powerful members of that guild are currently gathered on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:42.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?! They ain't nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like those...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll turn 'em all into ashes! {this guy always speaks in exclamations -yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suffocatingly hot as usual, Zancrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One should not underestimate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:03.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was for this day that I was bahrn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I concur, Capricorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let loose our desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be an all-out war for our guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shudder, shards of ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're speaking too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now explain what Hikaru just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I feel that way myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I will decipher what Rustyrose said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:36.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Desire is to want, and shard means heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meldy, can you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting... This is quite interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail! They do not yet know true darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate darkness that lies in the deepest depths...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart! The name itself means the heart of a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight we Devils will have sport with the Fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we devour them proudly, or be pound into dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is on, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave of Fairy Tail's founding master, Mavis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... Searching for a grave without even a hint! I haven't got a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the big problem, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there really no hints?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've participated in the exam 4 times in the past, so I've got a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's ever been an exam that was unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there has to be a hint hidden somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the second test is about brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:15.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain power, huh? Thinking of it that way, maybe the words themselves could hold a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The words?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Like for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We think that it's got to be a place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:27.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it could be interpreted as the "final stop of life".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so negative of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grave... Grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A keyword?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:39.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just hear something? Maybe it's my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll make this place your grave!", etc...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Marriage is the grave of one's life."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:51.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be something more Lucy-like you can think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "Even if people die, they become stars!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:14:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is that the way people picture me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it might not be that far off, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:09.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I bet I know where the grave is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a lucky one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! I bet Levy-chan will have solved this by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you guessed, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Lucy, but I think this second test is designed to test brain power and "how much you want it".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go! Let's follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:46.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't mind searching for them, but where did Wendy and Mest go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Juvia wanted to go cheer on Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I have to go my separate ways with Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unison Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong. In the end, you're the only partner for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By that I mean, become my life partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many children would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is all red, Juvia. Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, all is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia can barely stand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you'd like, why don't we split up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:26.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? If you stay that far back, we'll get separated ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that you're frightened of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time we fought during the first test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have held back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:47.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But being S Class isn't something to take lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed this exam a number of years ago, and it was a tough and difficult road.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:01.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you become S Class it's not all fun and games. You have responsibilities, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't sully the name of the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the weight you have to bear, and whatnot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words there's this and that, plus odds and ends, etc, etc...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia wants to go to where Gray-sama is, quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's painful to lose, that's for sure, but Juvia never really wanted to pass this test...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have gone too far with Lisanna, just back from Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people may call me childish, perhaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not hate you, not in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:31.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... I just want you to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's fine. Neither Juvia or Lisanna-san thinks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, if we could go our separate ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends sure are wonderful, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep working together from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we'll find Wendy and Mest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama is floating farther away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it, Mira-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've gotten better at cooking while in Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the Mira-nee over there was also good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really like a dream that the three of us can live together as siblings again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, isn't it a bit too salty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the way you chopped the vegetables could use some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So now is when you start complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chose a path? Find a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here 'cause I wanted to beat up Salamander or Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But these giant monsters are all so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:57.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't care what happens to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:05.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just fight with everything... You don't think anything of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's it? You think you can take me on, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:16.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'd better get big and strong to face me head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weak, that's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm small.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:27.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you get better things to do than get depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost already! Stupid Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him? And I thought maybe he wasn't so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:52.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a jerk... I hate him... I hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:10.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough findin' someone small like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:14.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest of the Black Guilds.... Why here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the master invited Dark Guilds to be part of the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:22.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that. These guys broke in from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:26.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, accidents happen on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And on S Class jobs, all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't get rid of a little accident like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could say you're qualified to be S class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're from Grimoire Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of the Baram Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:43.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't just attack us on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That'w  what's wrong with official guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rules in war-peron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,War?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:05.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Grimoire Heart Wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yomazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, Kawazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yomazu and Kawazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're after...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...to hunt the Fairies here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Dark Guild, Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of the legendary Black Wizard, they finally make their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before them lies Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as Natsu and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:45.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just turned it inside out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grave! S Class!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:53.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are all the men in my guild such idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The story that began with the S Class Advancement Exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...has begun moving in a direction no one could have ever predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:16.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle surrounding the legendary Black Wizard Zeref now is beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:59.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Righto! Let's have meat for lunch today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Meat again? I'd rather have fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get any power with fish. Gotta be meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.94,0:24:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, Natsu... You stubborn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if me and him went head to head I'd win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.04,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Soul of Iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you win butting heads against him, how hard is your head anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying I've got a hard head!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all out of gags here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:26.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
